Counter-Strike:Source - Map: de_romantic_nights2 - FINAL - by DesignerDrugV

Map Description:
This small map has two bomb places and an artifical canal. 
The roofs and buildings are supposed to give this map the freedom to choose your way. 
Terrorists may even have the chance to sneak around the Counter-Terrorists to plant the bomb.

Maximal players: 16

Test it and have fun with it!
